    dialPhoneNumber(this, myUserProfile.getPhone())
);
</code></pre> <p>As demonstrated in the code above, a call can be made by using <code>dialPhoneNumber</code>. Currently <code>IntentUtils</code> provides the following intents:</p> function detail dialPhoneNumber Dial number searchWeb Search specific content openWebPage Open the specified web page sendMmsMessage Send messages openEmail Send email createAlarm Create a alarm wifiSetting Open WIFI setting

